# Wanix WASI fixtures (Go)

Applies when editing Wanix WASI fixture sources, `build-wasm-go.sh`, or `tasks/groups/wanix.ts` wasm build tasks. See [`ops/fixtures/wanix/README.md`](../../ops/fixtures/wanix/README.md), skill `wanix-zed-cafe-export`.

## Policy

| Topic | Rule |
|-------|------|
| WASI drop fixtures | **Go only** — `ops/fixtures/wanix/wasi/<name>/main.go` |
| Build | `yarn task run wanix:wasm:build` → [`build-wasm-go.sh`](../../ops/fixtures/wanix/build-wasm-go.sh) |
| Toolchain | **Go** (`GOOS=wasip1 GOARCH=wasm`); no wasi-sdk, no wabt |
| zed-cafe export daemon | Separate module: `ops/fixtures/wanix/zed-cafe/` (`GOOS=js GOARCH=wasm`) via `wanix:zed-cafe:build` |

## Fixtures

| Package | Output | Role |
|---------|--------|------|
| `wasi/hello` | `hello.wasm` | one-shot stdout |
| `wasi/hold` | `hold.wasm` | infinite loop (term-write while running) |
| `wasi/termbridge` | `termbridge.wasm` | term bridge banner + hold |
| `wasi/zedcaferead` | `zedcaferead.wasm` | read `./zed-cafe/stats.json` |
| `wasi/zedcafewrite` | `zedcafewrite.wasm` | overwrite `stats.json` with `guestTouch` |
| `wasi/zedcafewritebad` | `zedcafewritebad.wasm` | schema guard negative (`evil.json`) |
| `wasi/zedcafelist` | `zedcafelist.wasm` | walk `./zed-cafe/` tree |

## Build tasks

| Task | Builds |
|------|--------|
| `wanix:wasm:build` | All Go WASI fixtures above |
| `wanix:zed-cafe:build` | `zed-cafe.wasm` (gojs export daemon) |
| `wanix:wasm:build:all` | `wanix:wasm:build` + `wanix:zed-cafe:build` |

## Prohibited

- New `.c` or `.wat` Wanix drop fixtures
- `wasi-sdk`, `wabt`, `build-wasm-c.sh`, `build-wasm.sh`, `install-wasi-sdk.sh`
- `wanix:wasm:build:c` task id (removed — use `wanix:wasm:build`)

## Allowed

- Go `wasip1` packages under `ops/fixtures/wanix/wasi/`
- Go `js/wasm` export daemon under `ops/fixtures/wanix/zed-cafe/`

Cross-link: rule `fixtures.mdc`, rule `wanix-term-bridge.mdc`.
